# Wacom
# Intuos Pro M
# PTK670
# (Third Generation)
#
# sysinfo.BSaGepftZP
# https://github.com/linuxwacom/wacom-hid-descriptors/issues/456#issue-2861784604
#
# Button Map:
# (A=1, B=2, C=3, ...)
#
#        A               E
#      D I B           H J F
#        C               G
#    *-----------------------*
#    |                       |
#    |                       |
#    |        TABLET         |
#    |                       |
#    |                       |
#    *-----------------------*
